title: NNormal Kjerag
technology: Technologies  MIDSOLE EExpure foam is engineered specifically for trail-running shoes that offers the best-possible propulsion and compression, less slippage, and way fewer blisters. OUTSOLE VIBRAM Litebase contains 3.5mm lugs and keeps sole weight down. VIBRAM Megagrip is super-stick and extra-durable.  UPPER Matryx Jacquard is exceptionally breathable and durable and is weaved from individually coated polyamide and Kevlar yarns.
